{"title":"rabbitmq","slug":"rabbitmq/rabbitmq","date":"2020-06-15T09:23:20.080Z","updated":"2020-06-16T09:27:19.193Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/rabbitmq/rabbitmq.json","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<p>进到<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/lib/rabbitmq</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>停止<br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rabbitmqctl stop_app</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>清空<br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rabbitmqctl reset</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>启动<br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rabbitmqctl start_app</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>添加账号<br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rabbitmqctl add_user qq 1234</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>分配角色<br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rabbitmqctl set_user_tags qq administrator</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>添加权限<br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rabbitmqctl add_vhost /qq</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>分配权限<br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\">